info: Vimeo, Inc. operates as a cloud-based software platform for professionals, teams, and organizations to create, collaborate, and communicate with video worldwide. Its platform enables subscribers to create, stream, host, distribute, market, monetize, and analyze videos online and across devices. The company serves creative professionals, small businesses, marketers, agencies, schools, nonprofits, and large organizations. Vimeo, Inc. was incorporated in 2020 and is based in New York, New York.
